Release 0.8.9, 30-January-2007

    - Database synchronization support
    - Implement adding and removing of cash from the Till
    - Improvements to the purchase order wizard
    - Support for canceling items and whole sales
    - Installation wizard improvements and bug fixes
    - Many improvements in the Till application
    - Creating a salesperson will really make him a salesperson
    - Discounts in purchase should be correct now
    - Updated and improved translations
    - Gift gertificate improvements
    - Country in person editor is now a combo
    - Creditcard and finance payments improvements
    - Much more, 121 bugs fixed!

    - Bugs fixed:

