Release 0.8.2,  11-October-2006

    - More robust First Time Configuration Wizard, many crashes has been fixed
    - ProfileEditor looks better and uses icons
    - Includes a copy of SQLObject, Formencode and dateutil
    - Till works properly on multiple machines
    - Sizegroups are moved to Glade files
    - Administration menu is no longer duplicated among all applications
    - PersonEditor looks better
    - ProfileEditor selects SalesPerson as default
    - Use Psycopg2 instead of 1, fixes a couple of crashes
    - Much improved testing coverage
    - Basic support for cloning a database
    - Many bugs fixed

    - Bugs fixed:

    #2195: Exceptions sent during the system initialization should be 
           notified in a dialog.
    #2268: Portuguese translation
    #2407: Improve the user authentication with PostgreSQL
    #2414: Remove administration menu from application glade files
    #2470: Configuration file error.
    #2688: Incosistency in the purchase order wizard.
    #2696: Document and test the gift certificate support.
    #2734: Stoq always references the till operation of the local station.
    #2756: Problems while cancelling a sale and trying to start it again.
    #2779: Wizard doesn't make it clear what to do if I /don't/ have...
    #2780: A crash in the first-time installation wizard took me bac...
    #2781: Don't suggest empty passwords -- or allow them.
    #2782: Clicking on New device in first-time wizard crashes.
    #2785: Multiple small fixes to Person creation dialog
    #2791: Add support for cloning a database
    #2792: Add a clone command to stoqdbadmin
    #2794: Stoq don't run at python version "2.4.4c0" as a string
    #2796: Use Psycopg2
    #2798: It is not possible to receive gift certificates.
    #2799: It is not possible to remove a delivery during a sale.
    #2809: Creating a delivery service using psycopg2 fails
    #2810: Wrong translation for editor's title.
    #2812: The sale discount isn't applied properly.
    #2816: Avoid sale opening for users who aren't a salesperon
    #2818: Include a button for sale printing in sales details dialog.
    #2820: Johans ProfileEditor improvments
    #2821: Product search report is broken.
    #2826: Problems with only-service sales.
    #2830: Do not show option for example database creation.
    #2831: Do complex Till operations in SQL
    #2833: Remove sizegroups from tilleditor.py
    #2835: First time wizard do not persist the administrator password.
    #2836: Remove sizegroups from python code
    #2850: Add ASalesPerson
    #2864: Use SelectResults.__nonzero__
    #2869: ProductSlave breaks when selecting a supplier
    #2870: A new user isn't created if not previous select a profile
    #2871: I can't send to supplier a purchase without money payment...
    #2876: Error when trying to create a new database
    #2877: Create a countries list in a combo.

